class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Run\\RunId"
type: readonly final class
summary: A value object representing a unique identifier for a run within the agent core domain. It encapsulates a string value to ensure type safety and immutability for run identification. This class supports string conversion and programmatic generation of new identifiers.
